des:
Kylie Jenner is one of the most recognisable and well know global superstars and icons. 
Star alongside her family on Keeping up with the Kardashians, CEO of her own mark up brand, social media queen and mother to Stormi you may think you know a lot about Kylie. 
Here on "Kylie Jenner - Could it be True?" learn some never heard before facts (and fiction) about Kylie.
What scares Kylie the most?
What does she think of her Mom?
What did her Dad teach her?
And who is Johnny?

While every fact is researched and triple checked, don't be getting yourself worked up if it proves to be wrong...at least it'll make you smile.

So sit down, relax and listen as we fill in those Kylie Jenner fact gaps!
